Our Team




Bernard (Bernie) Lanigan, Jr., CPA Chairman, Chief Investment Officer
Co-Founder of Southeast Asset Advisors, Inc.  Mr. Lanigan is also the Managing Partner and founder of Lanigan & Associates, P.C., Certified Public Accountants. (1974).  Mr. Lanigan is a graduate of Furman University.
 


 
C. Bradford Jackson, CPA, CFA President
Co-Founder of Southeast Asset Advisors, Inc.  Mr. Jackson has a BA in Economics from the University of Virginia and received a DBA with Honors in Business Studies from the London School of Economics.  He has additional course study at Florida State University.  Mr. Jackson is a licensed CPA in Georgia, Florida and Alabama.  He is responsible for portfolio management and asset allocation policy for Southeast Asset Advisors and works exclusively with high net worth clients.  He specializes in valuation services, income tax and estate planning. 



 
Mark C. Saussy, CPA, CFP, CIMA Executive Vice President
Mr. Saussy received a BBA from the University of Georgia.  Mr. Saussy has been with Southeast Asset Advisors since 2001.  His primary responsibilities include portfolio management, security analysis, client service, marketing and communication.  Immediately prior to joining Southeast Asset Advisors, he was vice president of corporate development for a NYSE Company.  He began his career at Price Waterhouse Coopers. 




 

Additional Directors



 
D. Mark Fletcher, CPA Director
Mr. Fletcher is a partner in Lanigan and Associates, P.C. Certified Public Accountants and Management Consultants.  Mr. Fletcher received his BS in Accounting from Florida State University in 1990 joining the firm in 1991.  He is a licensed CPA in Florida, Georgia and Alabama and specializes in timber / forest products and privately held businesses. 



 
Frank J. Mercer, CPA, CFP Director
Mr. Mercer is a partner in Lanigan and Associates, P.C. Certified Public Accountants and Management Consultants.  Mr. Mercer received his BS in Accounting from Florida State University and is a licensed CPA in Florida, Georgia and Alabama.  Mr. Mercer joined Lanigan and Associates in 1977 and is managing partner of the Tallahassee Office. 




 


